Long entry when RSI ≤ 30; exit at RSI ≥ 70. 100% equity per trade, 0.1% commission + 1 tick slippage. Optional 2% stop-loss. Visual buy/sell signals, dynamic SL line, and background highlight on oversold zones. Clean, backtest-ready Pine Script v5. Everything is easily adjustable to suit your liking.
